    "Id": 11,
    "Content": "Be sure to have tauri-cli installed: ```cargo install tauri-cli```\n</br>\n\n## Release signing\n\nmacOS release artifacts must be signed and notarized to avoid Gatekeeper reporting that the installed app is damaged. See [macOS signing and notarization](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RickyDane/CoDriver/master/docs/macos-signing-notarization.md) for required GitHub Actions secrets and verification commands.\n\n## Star History\n\n<a href=\"https://star-history.com/#rickydane/CoDriver&Date\">\n <picture>\n   <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date&theme=dark\" />\n   <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date\" />\n   <img alt=\"Star History Chart\" src=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date\" />\n </picture>\n</a>\n\n#### Other third party software\n- DragSelect (https://github.com/ThibaultJanBeyer/DragSelect)\n",
    "ContentSha": "Jdk3pRC3cChr4Ekku22QOob4zcA9XEYk6gCMKWQCNCs=",
    "SectionType": "",
    "StartLine": 0,
    "EndLine": 0,
    "Translation": "請確保已安裝 tauri-cli：```cargo install tauri-cli```\n</br>\n\n## 發行簽名\n\nmacOS 發行成品必須簽名並經過公證，才能避免 Gatekeeper 報告已安裝的應用程式損壞。請參閱 [macOS 簽名與公證](https://raw.githubusercontent.com/RickyDane/CoDriver/master/docs/macos-signing-notarization.md) 以取得所需的 GitHub Actions 機密及驗證指令。\n\n## 星星歷史\n\n<a href=\"https://star-history.com/#rickydane/CoDriver&Date\">\n <picture>\n   <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date&theme=dark\" />\n   <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date\" />\n   <img alt=\"星星歷史圖表\" src=\"https://api.star-history.com/svg?repos=rickydane/CoDriver&type=Date\" />\n </picture>\n</a>\n\n#### 其他第三方軟體\n- DragSelect (https://github.com/ThibaultJanBeyer/DragSelect)\n",
